  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.ServiceUnavailableTitle">Propagation service unreachable</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.ServiceUnavailableAction">The app tried to start the local propagation service automatically. Check that the service is built, or confirm the configured gRPC endpoint is reachable.</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.ServiceUnavailableDetail">Unable to connect to {0}. Diagnostic code: {1}. {2}</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.SolveFailedTitle">Propagation solve failed</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.SolveFailedAction">Open the Logs page to inspect propagation-service records around the failure, and verify the input parameters and service process state.</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.RpcUnavailableAction">Confirm the local propagation service is running, or verify that `TRAILMATE_PROPAGATION_GRPC_ENDPOINT` points to the correct address.</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.RpcUnavailableDetail">Endpoint {0} returned Unavailable. Low-level detail: {1}</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.RpcStatusTitle">Propagation service returned {0}</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.RpcStatusAction">Check the Logs page for propagation errors, and verify server inputs, version compatibility, and protocol compatibility.</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.RuntimeExceptionTitle">Propagation runtime exception: {0}</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.RuntimeExceptionAction">Check the Logs page for exception details, and confirm that the propagation service, contracts, and current UI build are aligned.</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.Detail.InvalidEndpoint">Configured endpoint is invalid. {0}</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.Detail.RemoteEndpointUnreachable">Configured endpoint is unreachable and is not managed locally. {0}</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.Detail.ManagedProcessUnhealthy">A local propagation service process exists, but its endpoint is still unavailable.</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.Detail.ServiceBinaryMissing">Propagation service executable was not found. Build `TrailMateCenter.Propagation.Service` first.</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.Detail.ServiceStartFailed">The propagation service process failed to launch.</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.Detail.ServiceStartTimeout">The propagation service process started, but the endpoint did not become reachable in time.</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.Detail.ServiceStartException">The propagation service failed during startup. {0}</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.SitesMissingTitle">Scenario sites are missing</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.SitesMissingAction">Right-click on the workbench to place a base station first, then add at least one target node.</x:String>
  <x:String x:Key="Ui.Propagation.Error.SitesMissingDetail">The solver does not auto-generate nodes anymore. A runnable scenario requires one base station and at least one target node.</x:String>
